[The food implicated in the transmission of salmonellosis in the boxed meals is not stated. Undercooked chicken or eggs are possible vehicles, but salmonellae can be found in many foods. It is also possible that poor kitchen hygiene could be responsible for the contamination.

Okazaki City is in Aichi prefecture located in the ChÅ«bu region of Japan, and the prefecture can be seen on a map at https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aichi_Prefecture.

